Title: Sunday Morning Linux Review Live  Broadcast
Presenters: Tony Bemus, Mary Tomich, Tom Lawrence
Book Description: This podcast is produced by 3 local people who also have been associated with Penguicon as speakers over the years. Their podcast recently was added to the player.fm list of Best Linux Podcasts. And as they have done since the beginning- they will do a live recording of their podcast at Penguicon.
